1. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with text mining and stop words, which are important concepts in information retrieval. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper focuses on developing a stop words list for Twitter, which is a language-based social media platform. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with analyzing Twitter data, which is a social network platform. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper discusses the development of text mining software and approaches for identifying and removing stop words. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new technique using combinatorial values, which is a machine learning approach.
